headline: Fastenal Debuts High-Tech Distribution Center in Magna, Utah
summary: WINONA, Minn., September 02, 2025--Fastenal Company (Nasdaq: FAST), a leader in industrial distribution and supply chain solutions, has begun operating in its newly-built distribution center in Magna, Utah, just outside the Salt Lake City metro area. Equipped with cutting-edge technology to streamline product intake, order picking, and shipping sortation, the 298,000 square-foot facility is designed to enhance operational efficiency and customer service throughout the region.
